   227→## Removed
   228→
   229→### Short option flag longer than a single character
   230→
   231→Short option flags like `-ws` were never supported, but the old README did not make this clear. The README now states that short options are a single character.
   232→
   233→- README updated in Commander v3.
   234→- Deprecated from Commander v9.
   235→- Throws an exception in Commander v13. Deprecated and gone!
   236→- Replacement added in Commander v13.1 with support for dual long options, like `--ws, --workspace`.
   237→
   238→### Default import of global Command object
   239→
